unslated imported paprika
regular paprika
cayanne pepper
black pepper
salt to taste
garlic
medley of diced bell peppers
flour
red wine
bacon
butter
diced onion
sour cream

let butter and bacon cook on high, but do not brown bacon. add garlic and bell peppers and let cook until tender. Add enough flour to mix where all the moister is gone from dish. remove from heat and add a full amount of red wine. Add back to heat and add the various spices. Let cook until desired consistancy. hit sause with a genorous amount of sour cream before plating.
